{
  "stem": "71.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, if he only save-- will save 10 to 20 children from the whole ghetto, he will be happy to show the world that he saved 20 children.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could have saved a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he almost did, didn't he?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If the war would have ended earlier, if the Germans, if he would not give so many people out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If the German-- when the Germans ask for, for that amount of people, he never said no.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if you could say to the Germans, no, I don't want to give you that amount of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He tried to have a lot of-- enough work for the people to be able to keep them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if somebody lost the parents, and this, it hurted-- although I was with my parents to the last minute-- we went to the-- out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were children that lost their parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were the first ones to send out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he knew-- he knew where these people are going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there were single people without parents, they should not have been punished for that, and be sent to Majdanek or Treblinka, or Auschwitz, or whatever they send them out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it might-- I think because he thought, in a way, sometimes, maybe, deep down in his heart he did not want to part a family.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did not want to send one person away from the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If it was a single person, he substituted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if, if he deserves to be, you know, rationalized like that-- that he did something good, because he really could do much better, or he could have resigned and give away to a younger person.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because-- Not that I condemned.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
